    类 说明
    AppInit
    This class will load init stage of the android app
    LogInActivity
    This class will load log in stage and do logic judgement for log in action.
    MainStage
    This class load the main stage which has three fragment to achieve different functions
    MapStage
    This part will load map stage that can achieve map functions in our app not finished yet

    This class will run basic config of app and store for some static variable
    Order
    The order class which include all information of a order.

    This part will load order stage which let user check their bill
